### 測試檔案 (REST Client)
### 請在 VSCode 中安裝 "REST Client" 擴充功能來執行以下請求

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@userId = 替換為實際的 user id
@taskId = 替換為實際的 task id
@reminderId = 替換為實際的 reminder id

### 1. 建立使用者
# @name createUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "name": "測試用戶",
  "lineId": "line12345"
}

### 2. 取得使用者資料
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

### 3. 建立任務 (同時包含排程提醒)
# @name createTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "title": "軟體工程期末報告",
  "courseName": "軟體工程",
  "description": "記得要附上架構圖",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-15T23:59:00Z",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "remindAt": [
    "2026-06-14T12:00:00Z",
    "2026-06-15T12:00:00Z"
  ]
}

### 4. 取得任務列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?userId={{userId}}&status=PENDING

### 5. 取得單一任務詳細資訊
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}

### 6. 更新任務狀態為已完成
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### 7. 新增額外的提醒
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/reminders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remindAt": "2026-06-14T18:00:00Z"
}

### 8. 刪除單一提醒
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reminders/{{reminderId}}

### 9. 刪除任務
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
